  <text fill="#3A2800" font-family="Arial,sans-serif" font-size="7" x="24" y="212">Los 118 elementos base del corpus SV. Dos</text>
  <text fill="#3A2800" font-family="Arial,sans-serif" font-size="7" x="24" y="223">familias: Σ₁ (convergente pura, k 01–058) y</text>
  <text fill="#3A2800" font-family="Arial,sans-serif" font-size="7" x="24" y="234">Σ₂ (exploratoria pura, k 059–0118). Perfil</text>
  <text fill="#3A2800" font-family="Arial,sans-serif" font-size="7" x="24" y="245">φ(k) = (EN_SV, r_SV, IP_SV, M_SV).</text>
  <text fill="#8B5A00" font-family="Arial,sans-serif" font-size="7" font-style="italic" x="24" y="254">Estatuto V · contrastable experimentalmente</text>
