  <text fill="#1A2A1A" font-family="Arial,sans-serif" font-size="7.5" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle" x="141" y="367">Qué es la Tabla Global</text>
  <text fill="#1F3050" font-family="Arial,sans-serif" font-size="7" x="24" y="379">Ω₄₄₃ = Tabla Cero ∪ Tabla 1 · 443 elementos.</text>
  <text fill="#1F3050" font-family="Arial,sans-serif" font-size="7" x="24" y="390">Dominio operativo del CPS-SV. Cada par no</text>
  <text fill="#1F3050" font-family="Arial,sans-serif" font-size="7" x="24" y="401">ordenado {A,B} ⊂ Ω₄₄₃ es un protopar Π(A,B)</text>
  <text fill="#1F3050" font-family="Arial,sans-serif" font-size="7" x="24" y="412">sobre el que opera U_SV → D(A,B).</text>
  <text fill="#1F3050" font-family="Arial,sans-serif" font-size="7" x="24" y="423">|Ω_proto| = C(443,2) = 97.903 protopares.</text>
  <text fill="#1A2A1A" font-family="Arial,sans-serif" font-size="7" font-weight="bold" x="24" y="434">Celda: EN_SV · M_SV% por elemento</text>
